% Regression pin for the type-table "float = unknown" flaw: an element
% scatter over array_dv[REAL] had its element port clobbered to
% sisal_array_t by pass2 propagation (integer elements were immune only
% because int32 read as "known").  Fixed by pass_edges: IF1 edge tags are
% locked as the scalar-type authority before any heuristic pass runs.

define f
type OneD = array_dv[real];
function g(x: real returns real)
  x + 1.0
end function
function f(v, w: OneD returns OneD)
  for vel in v
  returns array_dv of g(vel) + w[1]
  end for
end function
